ng nhị thập tứ thị ngự Khế tứ thập vận - 贈王二十四侍禦契四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BA%A1c-nh%C3%A2n-1/poem-o4EVPW8qBqGIiDBnjz0VQg">Thạc nhân 1 - 碩人 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/Thanh-minh/poem-XTyhYpf2RFsaTCBHf6koJA">Thanh minh - 清明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ki%C3%AAn/author-wRpSKwqTcKjFpinJIe2YPg">Hoàng Đình Kiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C4%83ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-mNOy3SNrg62IwI7dut3fVg">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C4%83ng/author-SoTHLJh5OjEBhbsajXk70A">Lương Tăng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-t%E1%BA%A3o-xu%C3%A2n/poem-UYeS7NGqFE_7ceNmH4moKQ">Trường An tảo xuân - 長安早春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/author-lb0C1LYxo0fcanV11dmAog">Mạnh Giao</a>)<br></div>	</div>
